---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
import FeatureBlock from '../components/FeatureBlock.astro';
---
<Layout title="Insight Hunter Standard: Cash Flow Forecasting for Startups | Financial Forecasting Tool">
  <head>
    <meta name="description" content="Insight Hunter Standard provides cash flow forecasting for startups with multi-entity support, AI financial forecasting tools, and integrated dashboards." />
    <meta name="keywords" content="cash flow forecasting for startups, financial forecasting tool, startup budget planning software, AI FP&A platform" />
  </head>

  <Hero />
  <section class="container">
    <p style="font-size:2.2rem; margin:60px 0 32px;">Insight Hunter Standard excels in cash flow forecasting for startups, serving as a robust financial forecasting tool for growing teams.</p>
    <p style="font-size:2.2rem; margin:60px 0 32px;">Insight Hunter Standard delivers comprehensive financial intelligence for growing teams, combining automation with secure integrations for real-time FP&A.</p>
    <p>This edition supports multi-entity consolidation, rolling 12-month forecasts, and automated alerts for burn or runway shifts. Sync with over 350 apps—including QuickBooks, Stripe, Gusto, HubSpot, and payroll systems—for seamless data flow into customizable dashboards. Track unit economics, margins by client or service, and revenue trends in one unified view.</p>
    <p>New features include driver-based budgeting, plan-vs-actual analysis, and investor-ready reports (P&L, balance sheet, cash flow) generated automatically. AI enhances natural language queries for deeper insights, such as ROI across channels or profitability by segment. Standard enables collaborative team access with basic roles, ensuring aligned decision-making.</p>
    <img src="/images/standard-mockup.png" alt="Standard integrated dashboard" class="feature-image">
    <p>Ideal for startups scaling operations, Standard provides the tools to modernize finance without complexity. For enterprise-grade AI CFO and human support, consider Full.</p>
    <a href="/shop" class="cta" style="display:inline-block; margin:60px auto;">Start Standard Trial</a>
  </section>

  <section class="container">
    <FeatureBlock title="Extensive Integrations" text="Automated syncing with accounting, CRM, and billing apps ensures real-time data accuracy across entities." image="/images/teams-mockup.png" alt="Integration overview" />
    <FeatureBlock title="Advanced Forecasting" text="Multi-scenario modeling and AI-driven predictions support strategic planning for growth." image="/images/ai-query-mockup.png" alt="Forecast scenarios" reverse />
  </section>
</Layout>
